<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcbbb2e94-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s41303"><num value="41303">§ 41303.</num><heading> Transfers of permits</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A permit issued under <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s41302">section 41302 of this title</ref> may be transferred only when the Secretary of Transportation approves the transfer because the transfer is in the public interest.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcbbb2e95-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1127">108 Stat. 1127</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
